==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Genevan
<hw>Ge*ne"van</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A native or
inhabitant of Geneva.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A supported of Genevanism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Genevanism</ent>⟦br⟧
